=========================================================
IS-A RELATIONSHIP
=========================================================

Inheritance represents an IS-A relationship.

Example:

Dog IS-A Animal
Car IS-A Vehicle
Manager IS-A Employee

=========================================================
HAS-A RELATIONSHIP
=========================================================

Represents Composition.

Example:

Car HAS-A Engine
House HAS-A Room
Computer HAS-A CPU

=========================================================
INTERVIEW QUESTION
=========================================================

Q. Which is preferred?

Answer:
Composition (HAS-A) is generally preferred over Inheritance (IS-A)
because it provides loose coupling and better flexibility.

